English.Text: Lack of belief forces your party to retreat. The chain suddenly stops moving forward, and the echoes of a disagreement at its head filter back. "Snap out of it! Keep moving!" "But sir, I swear, the thing had no eyes! I won't move another step!" Despite efforts to continue, the feeling your party are trespassing only intensifies, and they depart the dread rock drained and deeply perturbed.
